Author: katebishophawkguy
Text: if it helps one time the skinniest girl in my class was in a video and for some reason it made her look kind of chubby (i don’t know if it was the angle or what) and she was like omg is that what i look like?? without being able to help it and we were just like lmao no dude, we were ALL thinking wtf is up with that video because it’s in no way a reflection of reality

Text: This is why I never look at pictures that other people take of me because I just know I'm going to hate it
